<span style="color: orange;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong><span class="bbc_u">¿Cómo agregar BBcodes?</span></strong></span></span><br /><br /><strong>Paso 1:</strong> Nos vamos al archivo <strong>Subs.php</strong> (<em>root/Source/Subs.php</em>):<br />Buscar y clonar:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;array(<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;tag&#039; =&gt; &#039;spoiler&#039;,<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;before&#039; =&gt; &#039;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; background: #000000;&quot; onmouseover=&quot;this.style.color=\&#039;#FFFFFF\&#039;;&quot; onmouseout=&quot;this.style.color=\&#039;#000000\&#039;;&quot;&gt;&#039;,<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;after&#039; =&gt; &#039;&lt;/span&gt;&#039;,<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br /></code>Modificar<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;array(<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;tag&#039; =&gt; &#039;mytag&#039;, <strong><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><em>(es el nuevo tag)</em></span></strong><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;before&#039; =&gt; &#039;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; background: #000000;&quot; onmouseover=&quot;this.style.color=\&#039;#FFFFFF\&#039;;&quot; onmouseout=&quot;this.style.color=\&#039;#000000\&#039;;&quot;&gt;&#039;, <span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><strong><em>reemplazo para el inicio del tag</em></strong></span><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;after&#039; =&gt; &#039;&lt;/span&gt;&#039;, <span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><strong><em>reemplazo para el cierre del tag (no es imprescinbible))</em></strong></span><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br />Hasta aquí es suficiente para que funcione. Pero con los pasos 2 y 3 se introduce en la barra de bbcodes.<br /><br /><strong>Paso 2:</strong> Nos vamos al archivo <strong>Modifications.english.php</strong> (<em>root/Themes/default/languages/Modifications.english.php</em>) y/o (<em>root/Themes/tu-tema/languages/Modifications.english.php</em>):<br />Agregar en cualquier parte del archivo:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">$txt&#91;&#039;tu_tag&#039;] = &#039;Tu Tag&#039;;</code>Nótese que pueden traducir su tag si además de agregar la línea en <em>modifications.english</em> también lo agregan en <em>modifications.tu-idioma</em>.<br /><br /><strong>Paso 3:</strong> Nos vamos al archivo <strong>Subs-Editor.php</strong> (<em>root/Source/Subs-Editor.php</em>):<br />Buscar y clonar:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">array(<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;image&#039; =&gt; &#039;spoiler&#039;,<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;code&#039; =&gt; &#039;spoiler&#039;,<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;before&#039; =&gt; &#039;[spoiler]&#039;,<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;after&#039; =&gt; &#039;[/spoiler]&#039;,<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;description&#039; =&gt; $txt&#91;&#039;spoiler_post&#039;]<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),</code>Ubicar en el orden correcto según se desee ver.<br />Ahora a modificar la estructura según se les dicta a continuación:<br />array(<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;image&#039; =&gt; &#039;spoiler&#039;, <span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><strong><em>archivo .gif de la carpeta /themes/default/images/bbc/ ó /themes/tu-tema/images/bbc/</em></strong></span><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;code&#039; =&gt; &#039;spoiler&#039;, <span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><strong><em>es el tag que se pondrá en tu texto cuando presiones el botón, creo!!</em></strong></span><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;before&#039; =&gt; &#039;[ spoiler]&#039;,<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;after&#039; =&gt; &#039;[/ spoiler]&#039;,<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#039;description&#039; =&gt; $txt&#91;&#039;spoiler_post&#039;] <span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><strong><em>variable definida en modifications.english.php</em></strong></span><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),
